text: "Uprising" is a 2009 song by Muse. It is the leading single from their fifth studio album The Resistance. It went to the top 20 in the United Kingdom, Scotland, New Zealand, Switzerland, Norway, Belgium, Denmark, Finland, Sweden, Hungary, Italy and Ireland. It also made number 28 in Canada and number 37 in the United States. ==Track listing== ===7-inch=== *Warner Bros. — WEA458 ===CD=== *Warner Bros. — WEA458CD ===Download=== ==References== Category:2009 songs Category:Muse songs Category:Alternative rock songs Category:Glam rock songs Category:Electronic rock songs
